  "Description": {
    "English": "A specially tuned resonance jammer, designed to interfere with the remote <span class=\"name name-stellar\">cargo scans</span> deployed by system authorities in the search for <span class=\"name name-special\">smuggled goods</span>.<br><br>Deploy from the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Quick Menu</span> (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) while a scan is in progress to deflect the probe. Note: jamming is not 100% effective.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个经过特别调谐的共振干扰器，用于干扰星系当局为搜索<span class=\"name name-special\">走私货物</span>而部署的远程<span class=\"name name-stellar\">货物扫描</span>。<br><br>在扫描过程中从<span class=\"name name-technology\">快捷菜单</span>（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中部署以反射探测。请注意：干扰并非100%有效。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "經過特殊調頻的共振干擾器，設計用來干擾星系當局搜索<span class=\"name name-special\">走私物品</span>所部署的遠端<span class=\"name name-stellar\">貨物掃描</span>。<br><br>在進行掃描時，從<span class=\"name name-technology\">快捷選單</span> (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 部署，以反射探測器射線。注意：干擾並非 100% 有效。"
  },
